; **********************************************************************************
; Negative test for card maize-37, cross-ref maize-52: address_tokenizer's shared
; parse_literal helper used to silently drop a trailing unterminated value at EOF
; and return zero children, handing address_compiler an empty node that crashed
; dereferencing tree.value.begin() past end(). A bare ADDRESS keyword with no
; operand at all before EOF reproduces the same shape. mazm must now reject the
; truncation with a clean diagnostic instead.
; The test harness treats this file as ExpectAsmError: it passes when assembly fails.
; This file intentionally has no operand at all: EOF must land immediately after
; the ADDRESS keyword for the truncation to actually reproduce.
; **********************************************************************************

ADDRESS
